Package: utest
Title: Implementation of the Lind/Mehlum Utest
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jo Thori",
           family = "Lind",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "j.t.lind@econ.uio.no",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2980-3814"))
Description: An implementation of Lind and Mehlum's (2010) Utest to test for the presence of a U shaped or inverted U shaped relationship between 
              variables in (generalized) linear models. It also implements a test of upward/downward sloping relationships at the lower and upper 
              boundary of the data range.
